bama, Joe Biden, Elon Musk, Warren Buffett, Bill Gates were among the ones whose accounts were hacked in July. Even Twitter's own account was not spared by the hackers then.","title":"Modi\u2019s Twitter account hacked","url":"http://en.setopati.com/social/153820","video":[]}
